title: BRIEF-APN Property Group Says ‍HY Net Profit Attributable $9.6 Million ​

organizations.name: brief-apn property group says ‍hy net profit attributable

text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Apn Property Group Ltd:
* ‍HY NET PROFIT FOR PERIOD ATTRIBUTABLE TO MEMBERS $9.6 MILLION VERSUS $3 MILLION ​
* HY REVENUES FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES $14.6 MILLION, UP 18 PERCENT
* INTERIM DIVIDEND 1.25 CENTS PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
